               <p>London Cases, Before Mr. Recorder.</p>
               <p>5. 
               
                  <persName id="t18231203-5-defend113" type="defendantName">
                     JOHN 
                     BOWLES
                  <interp inst="t18231203-5-defend113" type="surname" value="BOWLES"></interp>
